org.turbogwt.net.http

Interface RequestSender<RequestType,ResponseType>

  • Type Parameters:
    RequestType - Type of data to be sent in the HTTP request body, when appropriate.
    ResponseType - Type of result from requests, when appropriate.
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    FluentRequestSender<RequestType,ResponseType>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    FluentRequestImpl

    public interface RequestSender<RequestType,ResponseType>
    Represents a class capable of submitting requests with content and receiving responses with content.
    Author:
    Danilo Reinert
